&lt;li&gt;Drive integrations with new data centers and third-party partners to expand inventory access and unlock new revenue streams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address scaling challenges as ContextGPT continues its rapid growth trajectory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal platform teams and external partners to make ContextGPT available at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take full ownership of systems end-to-end — from design through production operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive improvements in performance, reliability, and developer productivity across the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
