&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experienced senior backend engineer: &lt;/strong&gt;Strong in .NET Core (or a similar strongly typed language (Java, Kotlin, etc) and AWS, with a track record of designing and delivering complex production systems end-to-end&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems thinker:&lt;/strong&gt; Comfortable navigating a large, multi-product codebase and reasoning across service boundaries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ownership, Drive &amp;amp; Agency: &lt;/strong&gt;You take full responsibility for outcomes, not just tasks. You work independently, prioritize effectively, and proactively deliver high-impact results without waiting to be directed. This is the most important thing to us.&lt;/li&gt;
